machine-learning-causal-inference/temporal-fusion-transformer/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/temporal-fusion-transformer/</guid><description>系统介绍TFT模型的门控残差网络、变量选择网络与注意力机制，强调其在多变量多步预测中的可解释性优势。</description></item><item><title>不完全信息博弈：贝叶斯纳什均衡与类型空间</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/incomplete-information-bayesian-games/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/incomplete-information-bayesian-games/</guid><description>建立不完全信息博弈的Harsanyi类型空间框架，推导贝叶斯纳什均衡的分析方法，通过双边拍卖、信贷配给和贸易谈判等应用案例说明私有信息对均衡结果的深刻影响。</description></item><item><title>信号博弈：劳动力市场模型、精炼贝叶斯均衡与均衡选择</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/signaling-games-spence-model/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/signaling-games-spence-model/</guid><description>系统建立信号博弈的分析框架与精炼贝叶斯均衡概念，深入推导Spence劳动力市场信号模型的分离均衡与混同均衡，讨论均衡精炼标准与信号传递的本质逻辑。</description></item><item><title>动态博弈与子博弈精炼：序贯理性与承诺问题</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/dynamic-games-subgame-perfect/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/dynamic-games-subgame-perfect/</guid><description>系统建立扩展式博弈的分析框架，详解逆向归纳法与子博弈精炼纳什均衡的概念，通过最后通牒、入场威慑、连锁店悖论等案例阐明序贯理性与不可置信威胁的核心问题。</description></item><item><title>协整与误差修正模型：长期均衡与短期动态</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/cointegration-and-vecm/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/cointegration-and-vecm/</guid><description>讲解协整理论、Engle-Granger与Johansen检验、VECM建模及其在宏观金融长期关系分析中的应用。</description></item><item><title>双重差分法：平行趋势、异质性处理效应与交错DID</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/difference-in-differences/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/difference-in-differences/</guid><description>从经典2×2 DID出发，推导双向固定效应（TWFE）的识别条件，详解平行趋势假设的检验与强化策略，并系统介绍交错采纳设计下异质处理效应的新近文献（Callaway-Sant&amp;rsquo;Anna, Sun-Abraham）。</description></item><item><title>因果推断的潜在结果框架：Rubin因果模型与干预效应估计</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/potential-outcomes-framework/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/potential-outcomes-framework/</guid><description>系统阐述Rubin潜在结果因果模型（POF）的核心概念，包括因果推断的基本问题、SUTVA假设、ATE/ATT/LATE等处理效应概念，以及随机化实验如何从根本上解决选择偏差问题。</description></item><item><title>多Agent协作机制：角色分工、通信协议与一致性</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/generative-ai/multi-agent-cooperation-mechanisms/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/generative-ai/multi-agent-cooperation-mechanisms/</guid><description>介绍多Agent协作系统的组织方式、通信机制、任务分配算法与一致性保障，帮助构建可扩展的复杂任务执行系统。</description></item><item><title>多LLM竞争与机制设计：从博弈论到平台规则</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/generative-ai/multi-agent-competition-and-mechanism-design/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/generative-ai/multi-agent-competition-and-mechanism-design/</guid><description>讨论多LLM在共享平台上的竞争行为，分析竞价、声誉、激励相容与反合谋机制，为Agent平台规则设计提供理论基础。</description></item><item><title>多变量时序分析：VAR、SVAR与脉冲响应</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/var-svar-and-impulse-response/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/var-svar-and-impulse-response/</guid><description>系统讲解VAR与SVAR模型、Granger因果检验、脉冲响应函数与